<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,205,380,403]" pageId="13" pageNumber="658">Biology.</emphasis>
The 
<typeStatus box="[259,305,380,403]" pageId="13" pageNumber="658">type</typeStatus>
material was sifted from forest litter.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
